{"categories":["travel-leisure","events"],"collections":"","description":"Experience a seamless blend of elegance and functionality with this email template, perfect for travel or events promotion. Its one-column design, adorned with a dynamic countdown feature, keeps your messaging clear and impactful. The template's serene blue and white color scheme exudes a sense of calm, while the light background ensures your content stands out with clarity. The template's use of serif fonts adds a touch of sophistication, making it ideal for high-end promotions. Whether you're announcing an upcoming trip or a grand event, this template is designed to captivate your audience and keep them engaged until the very last second. It's more than just an email template; it's a beacon of light guiding your audience to your next big event.","short_description":"Unveil your next big travel or event promotion with this elegantly designed email template. Featuring a dynamic countdown, serene blue and white color scheme, and sophisticated serif fonts, it keeps your audience captivated and engaged. Ideal for high-end promotions.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Beefree_TemplateCatalog_ProfileImage_400x400_1.png","description":"A team of passionate designers, marketers, and technologists with an understanding that great design inspires action. At Beefree, we’re committed to creating responsive, mobile-friendly, and high-converting templates that empower teams to get more done with less time.","short_description":"","display_name":"Beefree Team","id":"beefree-team"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowP